OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778350335
OL,3,CVoters choose a different 'change' as
OL,4,CReform UK rout Labour in the North East
OL,6,FOur Political Correspondent Tom
OL,7,FSheldrick rounds up the local
OL,8,Felections results across the North
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,FSilksworth leisure centre in
OL,12,FSunderland has become a familiar sight
OL,13,Fon election nights, thanks to the
OL,14,Fspeed at which votes are counted.
OL,16,FNot normally because of the prospect
OL,17,Fof anything actually changing hands.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
