OL,3,CVoters choose a different 'change' as
OL,4,CReform UK rout Labour in the North East
OL,6,FReform figures on their new councils
OL,7,Fhaven't given much away - talking only
OL,8,Fof "a fresh approach" and how they
OL,9,Fwill "hit the ground running."
OL,11,FThe election has been dominated by
OL,12,Fnational and international issues,
OL,13,Ffrom the government's performance to
OL,14,Fthe conflicts in Gaza and Iran.
OL,16,FDelivering the local services people
OL,17,Frely on - from social care to bins and
OL,18,Flibraries - is where responsibility
OL,19,Fwill now lie for Farage's new foot
OL,20,Fsoldiers.
